Sample Calculations:
Delay calculation for 11.0592 MHz crystal

Resistor value calculation for LEDs (I = (5V - Vf)/R)

Pull-up resistor value for buttons (typically 10kΩ)

Baud rate calculation for serial communication

SAFETY PRECAUTIONS
Electrical Safety:

Always disconnect power before making connections

Use appropriate current limiting resistors

Avoid short circuits between VCC and GND

Component Safety:

Do not exceed maximum ratings (20mA per pin for 8051)

Use heat sinks if necessary for power components

Handle ICs with care to avoid static damage

Programming Safety:

Verify HEX file before programming

Use correct voltage levels (5V for 8051)

Follow proper programming sequence

